Susumu Terajima

810
01:45:03,297 --> 01:45:05,549
Ittoku Kishibe

811
01:45:10,137 --> 01:45:12,431
You didn't look very real
when you got shot.

812
01:45:12,598 --> 01:45:13,641
No?

813
01:45:16,644 --> 01:45:18,354
Have we got a place
to get changed?

814
01:45:18,354 --> 01:45:19,397
Yes.

815
01:45:20,022 --> 01:45:22,275
Don't worry.
I'll get rid of everything.

816
01:45:32,743 --> 01:45:33,995
I'm hungry.

817
01:45:34,578 --> 01:45:36,831
Want to stop somewhere
after we change?

818
01:45:36,831 --> 01:45:37,707
Yes.

819
01:45:37,707 --> 01:45:40,584
If we go in like this,
the old lady'll have a heart attack.

820
01:45:40,584 --> 01:45:41,794
The old lady...

821
01:45:42,169 --> 01:45:44,171
The last time we were all covered
in blood.

822
01:45:45,548 --> 01:45:46,882
That ain't too good...

